+# P4.10 — latency-contract dual-control exception approval
+
+P4.10 tightens P4.9 so a separate escalation ticket is no longer sufficient for **long** notifier silence overrides.
+
+## Goal
+
+If a deploy-lint purpose already exceeded the rolling silence budget / re-ack limit and the operator asks for a long suppression window, the override now requires:
+
+1. prepare request by operator A
+2. approve request by operator B (`B != A`)
+3. final `ack` by operator A with the approved `request_id`
+
+The rollout gate is still not disabled.
+
+## New env
+
+- `LATENCY_CONTRACT_DEPLOY_LINT_SILENCE_APPROVAL_PREFIX`
+- `LATENCY_CONTRACT_DEPLOY_LINT_SILENCE_APPROVAL_TTL_S`
+- `LATENCY_CONTRACT_DEPLOY_LINT_SILENCE_DUAL_CONTROL_MINUTES`
+
+If requested silence minutes are **below** `LATENCY_CONTRACT_DEPLOY_LINT_SILENCE_DUAL_CONTROL_MINUTES`, P4.9 behaviour stays the same.
+
+## Workflow
+
+Prepare:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m orderflow_services.latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_v1 prepare-override \
+  --purpose meta_cov_rollout_controller \
+  --operator alice \
+  --ticket INC-42 \
+  --escalation-ticket SEV-9001 \
+  --reason "need long notifier suppression during incident bridge" \
+  --minutes 480
+```
+
+Approve:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m orderflow_services.latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_v1 approve-override \
+  --request-id <request_id> \
+  --operator bob \
+  --reason "second operator approved long exception"
+```
+
+Commit final silence:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m orderflow_services.latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_v1 ack \
+  --purpose meta_cov_rollout_controller \
+  --operator alice \
+  --ticket INC-42 \
+  --escalation-ticket SEV-9001 \
+  --approval-request-id <request_id> \
+  --reason "approved long silence" \
+  --minutes 480
+```
+
+## Rules
+
+- second approver must differ from requester
+- approval is bound to `purpose`, `ticket`, `escalation_ticket` and `minutes`
+- final `ack` must be performed by the original requester
+- approved request is one-time and becomes `consumed` after successful ack
+
+## Audit events
+
+- `latency_deploy_lint_override_approval_prepared`
+- `latency_deploy_lint_override_approval_approved`
+- `latency_deploy_lint_override_approval_consumed`
+- `latency_deploy_lint_ack_silence_dual_control_denied`
+
+## Metrics
+
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_dual_control_required{purpose}`
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_dual_control_denied_total{purpose}`
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_dual_control_override_active{purpose}`
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_approval_pending{purpose}`
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_approval_ready{purpose}`
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_approval_age_seconds{purpose}`
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_summary_dual_control_pending_total`
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_summary_dual_control_ready_total`
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_summary_dual_control_override_gate_active_total`
